name: Some Guys Have All the Luck!

description:
The new team is put to the test when they must face off with a demonic foe...and betrayal from within.

The Roy Harper lead version of the Titans find their hands full with a Garfield Logan (Beast Boy) who has been possessed by a demon-seed from Raven.
name: The Final Change

description:
The possessed Changeling continues to pummel the new team. Luckily for the Titans, the new Green Lantern, Kyle Rayner, is on hand to help out.

Psimon of the Fearsome Five takes on the Titans at an opportunistic time. The current team is a little green behind the ears, especially with Gar Logan possessed by a Trigon-seed from Raven.
name: Psimon Psays..DIE!

description:
Green Lantern and Donna Troy team up with the New Titans to take on one of the team's oldest and most dangerous adversaries—Psimon!

Part Two of a Fearsome Five versus the Titans. Throw in Donna Troy and Kyle Rayner, and you get a real mess. The Raven storyline gets thrown on the backburner for this issue.
name: Psimon Didn't Psay You'd Win!

description:
As the Titans regroup from their battle with the villain Psimon, Raven gathers her new Brotherhood of Evil. What does this have to do with the Titans old allies/sparring partners Thunder & Lightning? Plus, the team welcomes back an old friend to the fold.

After Psimon has been subdued, with the help of Jarras Minion, the Titans take a issue breather. Unfortunately, Thunder and Lightning (part-time Titans) are also subdued, but by Raven. They will have further use to her in soon to come issues.
name: Downtime

description: Forever Evil Part 1 of 3: The seeds that Raven has been planting have finally started to form into, quite possibly, a team. They have a mission to take on the Titans, but at this point in time, only Mirage.
name: Forever Evil Chapter 1: Dark Titans

description:
"Forever Evil" part 2 of 3. Raven's army of darkness grows even stronger with the addition of Supergirl to its ranks. Can even the Titans stand against a cadre of their former allies and friends who have been seduced by the dark side?

Raven's complete team, with the assistance of Supergirl, take on the Titans.
name: Forever Evil Chapter 2: The Road To Hell

description: Ms. Isaacson's third grade class has about the coolest homework assignment in the world! They've won a contest to hang out with the Avengers for a day, and whether that means learning to rock climb with Spider-Man, or heading to the petting zoo with the Hulk, or having Storm teach them all about meteorology, it's going to be a great day! All except for how the Avengers get kidnapped by the Mandarin as a part of his bid to take over the world by harnessing the Avenger's individual powers into an unstoppable super robot while the kids are guarded by about the hungriest looking dragon in existence. Okay, that part reeks. And what part does Ant-Man play? Hint: it involves ants.
name: Ms. Isaacson's Third Grade Field Trip

description:
It was the most unusual catch the fisherman had ever seen: a robotic creation with a skull for a head! ROBOT 13 has no idea what or who it is, nor where it came from. All it knows is that it has an instinctual and irresistible drive to protect mankind from mythological creatures of destruction. In this pulse-pounding debut issue, you’ll witness this unlikely hero’s dredging from the ocean depths, and its life-or-death battle with a terrifying Kraken! Robot 13 does all he can to protect those who’ve discovered him, in the hope that in the process, he’ll discover who… and why… he is. It’s only the beginning of this epic hero’s journey… and you won’t want to miss an issue of this thrilling quarterly series!

The crew of a fishing vessel makes an unusual discovery, something like looks like the dead body of a diver in an old, unusual suit. Their discovery stirs something else up from the depths below, a huge, kraken-like creature that cuts a bloody swath through the crew. Luckily for the captain, the “dead diver” awakens, and armed with weapons from the boat and incredible strength, he rises to the defence of his rescuers.
name: Colossus! - Chapter 1
